OL,6,FA veteran from was "surprised and
OL,7,Fdelighted" to be invited to Buckingham
OL,8,FPalace where he was presented with his
OL,9,F100th birthday card from the King.
OL,11,FJim Miller, who turned 100 today (June
OL,12,F1st), landed on the Normandy beaches
OL,13,Fin June and took part in the to
OL,14,Fliberate occupied France and western
OL,15,FEurope.
OL,17,FHe said: "I was totally surprised and
OL,18,Fdelighted to be invited to Buckingham
OL,19,FPalace!
