OL,3,CD-Day veteran given 100th birthday
OL,4,Ccard by King Charles
OL,6,F"I am proud that I can still share my
OL,7,Fmemories with the generations that
OL,8,Fcome after me and thankful that young
OL,9,Fpeople are interested in what happened.
OL,11,F"I'm looking forward to attending the
OL,12,FRoyal British Legion's commemorations
OL,13,Fat the National Memorial Arboretum in
OL,14,FJune."
OL,16,FBorn in Hackney, now living in South
OL,17,FWales, Mr Miller served in the 11th
OL,18,FHussars during the Second World War.
