OL,3,CD-Day veteran given 100th birthday
OL,4,Ccard by King Charles
OL,6,FHe was called up at 18 years old and
OL,7,Fvolunteered for the Army after failing
OL,8,Fa hearing test for the Air Force.
OL,10,FDrafted into the Armoured Corps, Mr
OL,11,FMiller became a driver and wireless
OL,12,Foperator in armoured cars.
OL,14,FHe landed on Juno Beach on June 9 at
OL,15,Fthe age of 20, after arriving on the
OL,16,Fdeck of an American ship with armoured
OL,17,Fcars in the hold.
